text: Arnstein Raunehaug (born 17 December 1960) is a Norwegian former cyclist. He competed in the team time trial event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Norway Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bergen
